description: Russia-Ukraine War News LIVE Updates:  Russian forces are now only 32 kilometres (20 miles) away from Ukraine's second largest nuclear facility, the Yuzhnoukrainsk Nuclear Power Station in Mykolaiv Oblast, US Ambassador to the UN Linda Thomas-Greenfield has said.
